<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.01 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/html4/loose.dtd">   <html>  <head>  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html;charset=utf-8">  <title>Old in a sentence (esp. good sentence like quote, proverb...)</title>  <meta name="description" content="211+80 sentence examples: 1. The old goose plays not with foxes. 2. You can't teach an old dog new tricks. 3. Old birds are not caught with new nets. 4. Youth is a blunder; manhood a struggle, old age a regret. 5. An old dog will learn no new tricks."/>  <link href="/common/dedecms.css" rel="stylesheet" media="screen" type="text/css">  <style>  #content div{  	line-height:23px;font-size:14px;margin-bottom:15px;  }  #ad_marginbottom_0 div{  	margin-bottom:0px;  }  .hidden1{display:none;}  </style>  <script>  function q1(word){  	formQ.word.value=word;  	formQ.submit();  }  function upWord(word,action,word){  	var votedNumber=getCookie("votedNumber"+word);  	if(votedNumber!=null){  		alert("Have done up or down!");  		return;  	}  	var xmlhttp;  	if (window.XMLHttpRequest){// code for IE7+, Firefox, Chrome, Opera, Safari  		 xmlhttp=new XMLHttpRequest();  	}else{// code for IE6, IE5  		xmlhttp=new ActiveXObject("Microsoft.XMLHTTP");  	}  	xmlhttp.onreadystatechange=function(){  	if (xmlhttp.readyState==4 && xmlhttp.status==200){  		////返回后做事情  		var responseText=xmlhttp.responseText;    		//有异常.  		if(responseText!="" && responseText!=null){  		   alert(responseText);  		}else{  			var id_temp="wordUpTimes";  			if(action=="down"){  				id_temp="wordDownTimes";  			}  			var temp=document.getElementById(id_temp).innerText;  			var displayTimes=parseInt(temp);  			displayTimes=displayTimes+1;  			document.getElementById(id_temp).innerText=displayTimes;  			//cookie别设置太长,防止用户电脑中cookie太多哦  			setCookie("votedNumber"+word,"1",12);  		}  	  }  	};  	xmlhttp.open("POST","upDownWordDo.php",true);  	xmlhttp.setRequestHeader("Content-type","application/x-www-form-urlencoded");  	xmlhttp.send("action="+action+"&word="+encodeURIComponent(word)+"&rnd="+ Math.random());  }  </script>  </head>  <body>  <form method="post" style="display:none;" target="_blank" name="formQ" action="/wordQueryDo.php">  <input type="hidden" name="word"/>  <input type="hidden" name="directGo" value="1"/>  </form>  <div class="pageDiv" style="border: 0px solid blue;">  <script>  function trim(str){  　return str.replace(/(^\s*)|(\s*$)/g,"");  }  var strDefault="Please input any word...";  function queryCheck(){  	if(formQuery.vagueSearch.checked){  		///formQuery.q.value=encodeURI(formQuery.word.value+" site:sentencedict.com");  		formQuery.q.value=formQuery.word.value+" site:sentencedict.com";  		var temp=formQuery.action;  		formQuery.action="http://www.google.com/search";  		formQuery.method="get";  		formQuery.target="_blank";  		//为了wo参数不提交  		formQuery.word.disabled=true;  		formQuery.submit();  		formQuery.action=temp;  		formQuery.method="post";  		formQuery.target="_self";  		formQuery.word.disabled=false;  	}else{  		formQuery.word.value=trim(formQuery.word.value);  		var word=formQuery.word.value;  		if(word==""||word==strDefault){  			alert("Please input any word!");return;  		}  		formQuery.submit();  	}  	var temp="1";  	if(!formQuery.directGo.checked){  		temp="0";  	}  	setCookie("directGo",temp,12);  	var temp="1";  	if(!formQuery.vagueSearch.checked){  		temp="0";  	}  	setCookie("vagueSearch",temp,12);  }  function getCookie(name)  {  	var arr,reg=new RegExp("(^| )"+name+"=([^;]*)(;|$)");  	if(arr=document.cookie.match(reg))  		return (arr[2]);  	else  		return null;  }  function setCookie(cookiename,cookievalue,hours){  	var date=new Date();  	date.setTime(date.getTime()+Number(hours)*3600*1000);  	document.cookie=cookiename+"="+cookievalue+";path=/;expires="+date.toGMTString();  }  </script>  <div class="header">  <table width="100%" style="margin-bottom:4px;font-size:14px;" height=65 cellspacing=0 border=0 >  <tr>      <td width=100 valign="bottom" style="padding:0px;">        <a href="/">        <img src="/images/logo.jpg" style="vertical-align:bottom;margin-bottom:1px;border:0px solid #dddddd" alt="Sentencedict.com" height=50 width=150>        </a>      </td>      <td valign="bottom">  <form method="post" style="margin:2px;margin-left:10px;" name="formQuery" action="/wordQueryDo.php">  <input type='text' style='display:none;'/>  <input type="hidden" name="q" value="">  <input type="text" name="word" maxlength=100 style="float:left;margin-bottom:3px;width:360px;height:28px;line-height:26px;padding-left:6px;font-size:16px;border:1px solid #3D7A01;border-top:1px solid #67CD01;border-left:1px solid #67CD01;color:gray;"   size=20 value="Please input any word..." onfocus="if(this.value==strDefault){this.value='';this.style.color='black';}" onblur="if(this.value==''){this.value=strDefault;this.style.color='gray';}" onkeydown="if(event.keyCode==13){queryCheck();}"/>  <input type="button" style="float:left;width:70px;height:30px;margin-left:4px;cursor:pointer;font-size:14px;" onclick="queryCheck()" value="Search"/><div style="margin-top:10px;float:left;">&nbsp;<input type="checkbox" name="directGo" style="margin-right:2px;margin-bottom:2px;margin-left:2px;" value="1" checked>Directly to word page&nbsp;<span title="use vague search provided by google" style=""><input type="checkbox" name="vagueSearch" style="margin-right:2px;margin-bottom:2px;" value="1" onclick="if(this.checked){formQuery.directGo.disabled=true;}else{formQuery.directGo.disabled=false;}"/>Vauge search(google)</span>  </div>  </form>  </td>  </tr>  </table>  <script>  var temp=getCookie("directGo");  //此情况修改directGo的checked状态  if(temp=="0"){    formQuery.directGo.checked=false;  }  var temp=getCookie("vagueSearch");  //此情况修改vagueSearch的checked状态  if(temp=="1"){    formQuery.vagueSearch.checked=true;  }  </script>  <div class="module blue mT10 wrapper w963">  <div id="navMenu" style="background-color:#199507;border:0px solid red;background-image:url('/images/green_skin.png');background-position:0 -72px;background-repeat:repeat-x;">  <ul>  	<li><a href="/"><span>Home</span></a></li>  	<li><a href="/top1000/"><span>Top1000 word</span></a></li>  	<li><a href="/top5000/"><span>Top5000 word</span></a></li>  	<li><a href="/phrase/"><span>Phrases</span></a></li>  	<!--<li><a href="/conjunction/"><span>Conjunction</span></a></li>-->  	<li><a href="/game/"><span>Game</span></a></li>  	<li><a href="/getSImage.php"><span>Sentence into pic</span></a></li>  	<li><a href="/feedback.php"><span>Feedback</span></a></li>  </ul>  </div><!-- //navMenu -->    </div><!-- //module blue... -->  <div>  </div>  </div><div class="place" style="margin-top:8px;margin-bottom:0px;height:26px;line-height:26px;"><a href="/">Home</a> &gt; <a href="Old.html">Old in a sentence</a>  </div>  <div id="div_main_left" style="width:81%;float:left;margin-top:8px;border:0px solid blue;">    <div class="viewbox" style="width:auto;padding-bottom:0px">  <div class="title" style="padding-top:0px;line-height:56px;height:auto;overflow:visible;">  <h2 style="display:inline;">Old in a sentence</h2><!--(esp. good sentence)--><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="javascript:;" onclick="upWord('Old','up','Old')">up(<span id="wordUpTimes">0</span>)</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="javascript:;" onclick="upWord('Old','down','Old')">down(<span id="wordDownTimes">0</span>)</a></span>  </div>  <div class="info">Sentence count:211+80 <input type="checkbox" id="onlyStudent" value="1" style="width:17px;height:17px;" onclick="onlyStudent(this);" />Only show simple sentences<small>Posted:</small>2016-07-17<small>Updated:</small>2016-12-13</div>    <script>  function onlyStudent(this1){  	///alert(this1.checked);  	if(this1.checked){  		document.getElementById('all').style.display='none';  		document.getElementById('student').style.display='block';  		setCookie("onlyStudent","1",12);  	}else{  		document.getElementById('student').style.display='none';  		document.getElementById('all').style.display='block';  		setCookie("onlyStudent","0",12);  	}  }  var temp=getCookie("onlyStudent");  //此情况修改vagueSearch的checked状态  if(temp=="1"){    document.getElementById('onlyStudent').checked=true;  }  </script>    <div  id="content" style="border-bottom:1px solid #aaaaaa;">    <!--最大高度为105px,能显示5行多的样子-->  <div style="line-height:20px;float:none;margin-top:5px;margin-bottom:5px;margin-right:5px;padding:4px;background-color:#cccccc;border:1px solid #DCDDDD;max-height:105px;font-size:14px;overflow:auto;">  	<span style='float:left;display:block;'>Synonym:&nbsp;</span><span style='float:left;display:block;'><a href='javascript:;' onclick='q1("abandoned");'>abandoned</a>,&nbsp;</span><span style='float:left;display:block;'><a href='javascript:;' onclick='q1("aged");'>aged</a>,&nbsp;</span><span style='float:left;display:block;'><a href='javascript:;' onclick='q1("ancient");'>ancient</a>,&nbsp;</span><span style='float:left;display:block;'><a href='javascript:;' onclick='q1("antique");'>antique</a>,&nbsp;</span><span style='float:left;display:block;'><a href='javascript:;' onclick='q1("elderly");'>elderly</a>,&nbsp;</span><span style='float:left;display:block;'><a href='javascript:;' onclick='q1("former");'>former</a>,&nbsp;</span><span style='float:left;display:block;'><a href='javascript:;' onclick='q1("mature");'>mature</a>,&nbsp;</span><span style='float:left;display:block;'><a href='javascript:;' onclick='q1("obsolete");'>obsolete</a>,&nbsp;</span><span style='float:left;display:block;'><a href='javascript:;' onclick='q1("outworn");'>outworn</a>,&nbsp;</span><span style='float:left;display:block;'><a href='javascript:;' onclick='q1("stale");'>stale</a>.&nbsp;</span><span style='float:left;display:block;'>Antonym:&nbsp;</span><span style='float:left;display:block;'><a href='javascript:;' onclick='q1("new");'>new</a>,&nbsp;</span><span style='float:left;display:block;'><a href='javascript:;' onclick='q1("young");'>young</a>.&nbsp;</span><span style='float:left;display:block;'>Similar words:&nbsp;</span><span style='float:left;display:block;'><a href='fold.html' target='_blank'>fold</a>,&nbsp;</span><span style='float:left;display:block;'><a href='hold.html' target='_blank'>hold</a>,&nbsp;</span><span style='float:left;display:block;'><a href='odd.html' target='_blank'>odd</a>,&nbsp;</span><span style='float:left;display:block;'><a href='add.html' target='_blank'>add</a>,&nbsp;</span><span style='float:left;display:block;'><a href='aid.html' target='_blank'>aid</a>,&nbsp;</span><span style='float:left;display:block;'><a href='all.html' target='_blank'>all</a>,&nbsp;</span><span style='float:left;display:block;'><a href='and.html' target='_blank'>and</a>,&nbsp;</span><span style='float:left;display:block;'><a href='bad.html' target='_blank'>bad</a>.&nbsp;</span><span style='float:left;display:block;'>Meaning:&nbsp;[əʊld]&nbsp;n. past times (especially in the phrase `in days of old'). adj. 1. (used especially of persons) having lived for a relatively long time or attained a specific age 2. of long duration; not new 3. (used for emphasis) very familiar 4. just preceding something else in time or order 5. of a very early stage in development 6. old in experience 7. belonging to some prior time 8. (used informally especially for emphasis).&nbsp;</span></div>  <div id="img1" style="margin:5px;margin-top:8px;float:right;">  	<img src="http://sentencedict.com/wordimage/172.jpg" style="width:300px;height:210px;" />  	<div style="text-align:center;margin-top:4px;font-size:12px;line-height:normal;margin-bottom:0px;width:280px;">Sentencedict.com random good picture</div>  </div>    <!--如果仅显示学生,并且该页有学生句子-->  <div id="all" >  <div>1. The <em>old</em> goose plays not with foxes.&nbsp;<a href='/s/42006.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>2. You can't teach an <em>old</em> dog new tricks.&nbsp;<a href='/s/48171.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>3. <em>Old</em> birds are not caught with new nets.&nbsp;<a href='/s/41650.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>4. Youth is a blunder; manhood a struggle, <em>old</em> age a regret.&nbsp;<a href='/s/44245.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>5. An <em>old</em> dog will learn no new tricks.&nbsp;<a href='/s/42554.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>6. Don't put new wine into <em>old</em> bottles.&nbsp;<a href='/s/47899.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>7. It is never too <em>old</em> to learn.&nbsp;<a href='/s/41284.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div id="ad_marginbottom_0" style="margin-top:-10px;margin-bottom:5px;"><script async src="//pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js"></script><!-- 728_90_20170421 --><ins class="adsbygoogle" style="display:inline-block;width:728px;height:90px" data-ad-client="ca-pub-7200850114163593" data-ad-slot="2392632666"></ins><script>(adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});</script></div><div>8. A young twig is easier twisted than an <em>old</em> tree.&nbsp;<a href='/s/40572.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>9. No man is so <em>old</em>, but thinks he may yet live another year.&nbsp;<a href='/s/43457.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>10. No fool like an <em>old</em> fool.&nbsp;<a href='/s/41579.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>11. If the <em>old</em> dog barks, he gives counsel.&nbsp;<a href='/s/41187.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>12. Prudence is a rich ugly <em>old</em> maid courted by Incapacity.&nbsp;<a href='/s/46915.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>13. No fool to the <em>old</em> fool.&nbsp;<a href='/s/41580.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>14. There is life in the <em>old</em> dog yet.&nbsp;<a href='/s/43953.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>15. There is no better looking-glass than an <em>old</em> friend.&nbsp;<a href='/s/42035.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>16. A colt you may break, but an <em>old</em> horse you never can.&nbsp;<a href='/s/40275.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>17. We hope to grow <em>old</em>, yet we fear old age; that is, we are willing to live, and afraid to die.&nbsp;<a href='/s/44104.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>18. There's many a good tune played on an <em>old</em> fiddle.&nbsp;<a href='/s/43967.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>19. Never too <em>old</em> (or late) to learn.&nbsp;<a href='/s/43437.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>20. If you wish good advice, consult an <em>old</em> man.&nbsp;<a href='/s/43107.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>20. Wish you can benefit from our online sentence dictionary and make progress every day!</div><div>21. A man is not <em>old</em> as long as he is seeking something. A man is not old until regrets take the place of dreams.&nbsp;<a href='/s/46930.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>22. An <em>old</em> physician, and a young lawyer.&nbsp;<a href='/s/40489.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>23. To make good use of life.one should have in youth the experience of advanced years,and in <em>old</em> age the vigor of youth.&nbsp;<a href='/s/47262.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>24. Learning is an ornament in prosperity, a refuge in adversity, and a provision in <em>old</em> age.&nbsp;<a href='/s/43247.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>25. When society requires to be rebuilt, there is no use attempting to rebuild it on the <em>old</em> plan.&nbsp;<a href='/s/47167.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>26. If you lie upon roses when young, you'll lie upon thorns when <em>old</em>.&nbsp;<a href='/s/43099.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>27. The follies of youth are food for repentance in <em>old</em> age.&nbsp;<a href='/s/41954.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>28. Knowledge is a comfortable and necessary retreat and shelter for us in an advanced age; and if we do not plant it when young, it will give us no shade when we grow <em>old</em>.&nbsp;<a href='/s/43226.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div>29. In youth the hours are golden in mature years they are silver, in <em>old</em> age they are leaden.&nbsp;<a href='/s/43145.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div><div style="margin-bottom:3px;">30. He who will not learn when he is young will regret it when he is <em>old</em>.&nbsp;<a href='/s/41134.html' target='blank' title='into the page of the sentence'><img src='/images/enter.jpg' style='vertical-align:bottom'/></a></div></div><!--all结束-->  <!--如果不是仅显示学生,或该页没有学生句子-->  <div id="student" style='display:none;'>  <div>1. Cathy's an <em>old</em> pro at organizing raffles.</div><div>2. Let's discard some of these <em>old</em> newspapers.</div><div>3. Try not to revert to your <em>old</em> eating habits.</div><div>4. As the <em>old</em> cock crows, the young cock learns.</div><div>5. That <em>old</em> temple is hidden among trees.</div><div>6. The story recalled <em>old</em> faces to my mind.</div><div>7. The supermarket has installed recycling bins for <em>old</em> newspapers, bottles and cans.</div><div>8. The <em>old</em> bus started with a jerk.</div><div>9. Let's discard some of these <em>old</em>.</div><div>10. It is a tradition that the young look after the <em>old</em> in their family.</div><div>11. You're getting quite romantic in your <em>old</em> age!</div><div>12. Alex is too young to be already thinking of herself as an <em>old</em> maid.</div><div>13. The <em>old</em> lady run three circuits of the track every morning.</div><div>14. The <em>old</em> couple lived a life of ease.</div><div>15. He's only 24 years <em>old</em> and a drug addict.</div><div>16. Pretending he doesn't remember is an <em>old</em> trick of his.</div><div>17. She has lost none of her <em>old</em> sparkle as a jazz singer.</div><div>18. He's a cunning/sly/wily <em>old</em> fox.</div><div>19. She's getting <em>old</em> and she tends to ramble a bit.</div><div>20. The <em>old</em> man looked cross and unfriendly.</div><div>20. Wish you can benefit from our online sentence dictionary and make progress every day!</div><div>21. The firefighter broke into the house to rescue the <em>old</em>.</div><div>22. He had met his <em>old</em> lady when he was a house painter and she was a waitress.</div><div>23. Smith is an <em>old</em> friend of mine.</div><div>24. At 20 years <em>old</em> he was not as agile as he is now.</div><div>25. The <em>old</em> should be well respected.</div><div>26. Let's chuck all these <em>old</em> papers and magazines away!</div><div>27. He played the role of the <em>old</em> king in our play.</div><div>28. The <em>old</em> man lived in a cottage on the side of the hill.</div><div>29. Is Bob an <em>old</em> friend of yours?</div><div style="margin-bottom:3px;">30. It is difficult for the <em>old</em> man to adjust to city life.</div></div><!--student结束-->    <div id="ad_marginbottom_0" style="padding-top:0px;margin-bottom:6px;line-height:normal;margin-top:-8px;">  <script async src="//pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js"></script>  <!-- 728_90_20170421 -->  <ins class="adsbygoogle"       style="display:inline-block;width:728px;height:90px"       data-ad-client="ca-pub-7200850114163593"       data-ad-slot="2392632666"></ins>  <script>  (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});  </script>  </div>  <div style="margin-bottom:3px;font-size:13px;line-hei